OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1779217874
OL,3,C'Strong case' for Bradford to be
OL,4,Cinvestigated in Grooming Gangs Inquiry
OL,6,FThe chair of the Grooming Gangs
OL,7,FInquiry has said there is a "strong
OL,8,Fcase" for Bradford to be included in a
OL,9,Fseries of investigations into local
OL,10,Fareas.
OL,12,FBaroness Anne Longfield, who lives in
OL,13,Fthe area, told the Home Affairs
OL,14,FCommittee "the Bradford case is
OL,15,Fobviously strongly made by many
OL,16,Fpeople, victims and survivors over
OL,17,Ftime...we're well aware of the case
OL,18,Fthat's been made and it's a strong
OL,19,Fcase."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1779217874
OL,3,C'Strong case' for Bradford to be
OL,4,Cinvestigated in Grooming Gangs Inquiry
OL,6,FShe added an announcement would be
OL,7,Fmade in six weeks.
OL,9,FAccording to a House of Commons
OL,10,Fbriefing "The inquiry will co-ordinate
OL,11,Finvestigations in certain local areas,
OL,12,Fthough it will not investigate every
OL,13,Farea where grooming gangs have
OL,14,Foperated."
OL,16,FIt came after questioning by Keighley
OL,17,Fand Ilkley MP Robbie Moore who has
OL,18,Fbeen pushing for Bradford to be one of
OL,19,Fthe areas the inquiry looks at.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1779217874
OL,3,C'Strong case' for Bradford to be
OL,4,Cinvestigated in Grooming Gangs Inquiry
OL,6,FHe said "I've consistently raised the
OL,7,FBradford district, commenting that I
OL,8,Fsuspect it will dwarf that of other
OL,9,Fareas
OL,11,F"What are you waiting for to be able
OL,12,Fto announce Bradford and Keighley
OL,13,Fbeing included as part of your local
OL,14,Finquiries", he asked.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
