FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1779217874
OL,3,C'Strong case' for Bradford to be
OL,4,Cinvestigated in Grooming Gangs Inquiry
OL,6,FOne of the inquiry's panellists,
OL,7,FEleanor Kelly, replied that if they
OL,8,Fannounced an investigation into the
OL,9,Farea now they would "be able to be
OL,10,Fjudicially reviewed by Bradford that
OL,11,Fwe had selected them on the basis of
OL,12,Fcriteria we had not yet established.
OL,14,FShe added any judicial review would
OL,15,F"delay" the process.
OL,17,FThe government committed to an inquiry
OL,18,Fin June 2025 and Baroness Longfield,
OL,19,Fthe former Children's Commissioner,
OL,20,Fwas appointed as the chair in December
OL,21,Flast year.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1779217874
OL,3,C'Strong case' for Bradford to be
OL,4,Cinvestigated in Grooming Gangs Inquiry
OL,6,FIt is due to last up to three years
OL,7,Fwith a budget of #65 million.
OL,9,FBut some victims and survivors have
OL,10,Fcriticised the process and the time it
OL,11,Fhas taken.
OL,13,FIn Tuesday's hearing, Baroness
OL,14,FLongfield said "we want to bring about
OL,15,Fnot only change but meaningful change,
OL,16,Fwe don't think there should be another
OL,17,Finquiry after this."
OL,19,FThose behind the inquiry say they will
OL,20,Fnot avoid difficult questions and
OL,21,Ftopics during their investigation.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
