FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1779217874
OL,3,C'Strong case' for Bradford to be
OL,4,Cinvestigated in Grooming Gangs Inquiry
OL,6,FAnother panellist, Zoe Billingham,
OL,7,Ftold the committee, "We're going to be
OL,8,Fforensically looking at how religion,
OL,9,Fculture, heritage and background could
OL,10,For could not have been a driver".
OL,12,FA Home Office spokesperson said: "The
OL,13,Fgrooming gangs scandal is one of the
OL,14,Fdarkest moments in our country's
OL,15,Fhistory ` where the most vulnerable
OL,16,Fpeople were abused and exploited at
OL,17,Fthe hands of evil child rapists.
OL,26,@nD@VxrtD@bOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
