PN,36107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1779217874
OL,3,C'Strong case' for Bradford to be
OL,4,Cinvestigated in Grooming Gangs Inquiry
OL,6,F"The independent national Inquiry has
OL,7,Fbegun its crucial work to uncover how
OL,8,Fthese crimes were allowed to happen
OL,9,Fand root out failure wherever it
OL,10,Foccurred.
OL,12,F"The Chair and Home Secretary have
OL,13,Fagreed that the Inquiry will be laser
OL,14,Ffocused on grooming gangs and will
OL,15,Fexplicitly examine the role of
OL,16,Fethnicity, religion and culture of the
OL,17,Foffenders and in the response of
OL,18,Finstitutions.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
